 the expansion center model, the obtained\nnew relativistic q0 agrees with the value q0=+2 inferred from the ECM paper I\neq. (41), when R0 is the proper distance at t0 of the expansion center from the\nGalaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2011 17:50:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2011 18:40:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2011 18:44:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 20 Sep 2012 17:02:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-21"}
