\nand geometry, and the observing design. The Hubble data processing and products\nare described in a companion paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2011 21:42:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 May 2011 19:54:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2011 00:39:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
