 gradual\ntransition. Hunting-gathering and agropastoral life style coexisted for a long\ntime and agriculture was adopted slowly into the existing subsistence scheme.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 May 2011 07:50:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2011 19:34:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-25"}
